-- ── Article 2: 1xBet ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
(
  'how-to-register-1xbet-kenya-2026',
  'How to Register on 1xBet Kenya 2026 — Welcome Bonus, M-PESA Deposit Guide and Free Football Predictions',
  'How to register on 1xBet Kenya in 2026, claim the welcome bonus, and deposit via M-PESA. Free football predictions and daily booking codes from MyFreeTip included.',
  E'1xBet is one of the most widely used international betting platforms among Kenyan football bettors. It carries a first-deposit welcome bonus, full M-PESA support, and some of the deepest football market coverage available in Kenya — from Premier League through to KPL and AFCON qualifiers.\n\nMyFreeTip recommends 1xBet as the natural second account alongside Paripesa for serious bettors who want to compare odds across platforms and access the widest possible range of football markets. If you are registering for the first time, this guide covers every step.\n\nHow to Register on 1xBet Kenya\n\nRegistration takes under three minutes. Go to 1xBet via the link on myfreetip.com. This connects your account to the MyFreeTip affiliate and unlocks booking code access on the site.\n\nStep 1 — Open the registration page. Tap Register on the 1xBet homepage. Select registration by phone number — the fastest option for Kenyan users.\n\nStep 2 — Enter your mobile number. Use the number linked to your M-PESA account so deposits and withdrawals route correctly.\n\nStep 3 — Select your currency. Choose Kenyan Shilling (KES). This sets M-PESA as your primary payment method and ensures your balance displays in KES.\n\nStep 4 — Create a password and complete registration. Your 1xBet account is active immediately. No document upload is required to start.\n\nStep 5 — Make your first deposit before placing bets. Deposit first to activate the welcome bonus. If you place a bet before depositing, you may not qualify for the bonus offer.\n\nKYC document verification is only triggered by withdrawals above certain thresholds — not at registration or on standard deposits. You can register, deposit, and bet without uploading ID.\n\nHow to Claim the 1xBet Welcome Bonus Kenya 2026\n\nAfter completing registration, go to Deposit in your account. Select M-PESA. Enter your first deposit amount — the welcome bonus is calculated as a percentage of your first deposit up to the maximum offer available.\n\nConfirm the deposit on your phone with your M-PESA PIN. Funds arrive in your 1xBet account within seconds. The welcome bonus is credited automatically — no bonus code or customer service contact required.\n\nWelcome bonus terms change regularly. The bonus is subject to wagering requirements before withdrawal — bonus funds must be turned over a specified number of times on qualifying markets. Always verify current bonus amount and conditions directly on the 1xBet platform before your first deposit.\n\nHow to Make an M-PESA Deposit on 1xBet\n\nIn your 1xBet account, tap Deposit and select M-PESA from the payment methods. Enter the deposit amount and confirm. A payment prompt appears on your phone — enter your M-PESA PIN to authorise. Funds appear in your 1xBet balance within seconds.\n\nThe minimum deposit via M-PESA on 1xBet is low and accessible for regular bettors. Withdrawals follow the same process through the Withdraw section — select M-PESA, enter the amount, and confirm. Standard withdrawals process quickly under normal conditions.\n\nHow to Use 1xBet Booking Codes\n\nA booking code loads a complete pre-built betting slip into your 1xBet account instantly. You enter one short code and the entire accumulator — every selection, every odd — appears ready to stake. No manual searching, no building the slip from scratch.\n\nTo load a booking code on 1xBet: open the app, tap the coupon or betslip icon at the bottom of the screen, find the Load Bet or Bet Code option in the panel, enter the code exactly as shown, and tap Load. Your full slip appears. Set your stake and confirm the bet.\n\nMyFreeTip publishes daily 1xBet booking codes for Premier League, Champions League, La Liga, Serie A, and African league fixtures. Get today''s codes and full predictions at myfreetip.com. Codes expire at kick-off — load before the first match on the slip starts.\n\n1xBet Football Market Coverage\n\nWhere 1xBet separates itself from most platforms in Kenya is market depth. Standard markets — Match Result, Over/Under Goals, Both Teams to Score, Double Chance, Asian Handicap, Correct Score — are available across all major European leagues and beyond.\n\n1xBet also covers KPL, AFCON qualifiers, CAF Champions League, and regional African football extensively. For Kenyan bettors who follow local and continental football alongside the European leagues, this breadth is a genuine advantage. The live betting section is also one of the strongest available in Kenya, with fast odds updates across concurrent matches.\n\n1xBet App — Download and Setup on Android\n\nThe 1xBet Android app is available directly from the 1xBet website. Like Paripesa, it is not listed on the Google Play Store due to app store gambling restrictions. Download from the official 1xBet site, enable installation from unknown sources in your Android security settings if prompted, and install.\n\nThe app is feature-rich — more complex to navigate than Paripesa due to the volume of markets available, but experienced bettors find this a strength. Football is the primary sport and is prominently placed in the navigation. Booking code entry is in the coupon section, clearly labelled.\n\nFrequently Asked Questions\n\nIs 1xBet available in Kenya? Yes. 1xBet accepts Kenyan users, supports M-PESA deposits and withdrawals, and is one of the most widely used international betting platforms among Kenyan football bettors. Verify current licensing and regulatory status directly on the 1xBet website.\n\nHow do I withdraw from 1xBet to M-PESA? Go to Withdraw in your account, select M-PESA, enter the withdrawal amount, and confirm. Standard withdrawals are processed quickly. First-time or larger withdrawals may require KYC verification — have your national ID ready if you are withdrawing a significant amount for the first time.\n\nWhat is the minimum deposit on 1xBet Kenya via M-PESA? 1xBet offers one of the lowest minimum M-PESA deposits among major platforms operating in Kenya. The exact minimum is displayed on the deposit page in your account. It is accessible for regular bettors managing their bankroll across multiple platforms.\n\nHow do I get free football predictions to use with my 1xBet account? MyFreeTip publishes free daily football predictions, match analysis, and 1xBet booking codes at myfreetip.com — no subscription, no payment, no VIP required. Register on 1xBet via myfreetip.com to unlock booking codes on the site. Get daily picks sent directly via the Telegram community.\n\nThis content is for informational and entertainment purposes only. 18+ only. Please gamble responsibly. Past performance does not guarantee future outcomes.',
